<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣看著蟲蟲，<delay20 />
時間就會不知不覺地溜走耶～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明明是吃過飯才來的，<delay20 />
但等到我發現的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />肚子卻在叫～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />地上的小蟲蟲看到的我<delay20 />
是長什麼樣子呢～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能會因為我太大<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以看不到臉吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這裡比籠子裡還要大，<delay20 />
所以蟲蟲們可以盡情活動，<delay8 />
大家看起來都很開心耶～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說一動也不動的蟲蟲，<delay20 />
是不是在想什麼事情呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說今天要吃什麼<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸嘿嘿～<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟我一樣耶～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有些蟲蟲幾乎不會動對吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會以為<delay8 />我們會把牠們當成玩具，<delay20 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />趁機監視我們吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這裡<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很暖和很舒服耶～<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣子<delay20 />感覺就像是在對我說，<delay20 />
請在這裡睡午覺～<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果可以在這裡練習捕蟲，<delay20 />
感覺可以進步一點點的說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是一定會被<colour id="3" />傅達<colour id="65535" />罵的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這裡很暖和，<delay20 />
所以蟲蟲也都活蹦亂跳的，<delay8 />
看起來很舒服喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我原本是來看蟲蟲的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因為這裡很暖和很舒服，<delay20 />
我<delay20 />不知不覺地就<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Sleep" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="100" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這裡的蟲蟲們<delay20 />
大～家都是<tag a="110" b="33" />的<delay8 />
好朋友喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這裡有蟲蟲<delay20 />也有花朵，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很喜歡這裡喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這裡的蟲蟲們<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來很開心吧～？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為島上的所有人都很愛護牠們喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我期待已久的<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
終於開幕了，<delay20 />
所以我很高興喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了不要錯過新來的蟲蟲，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我打算每天都來看喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聽說<delay8 />這座島上蓋了<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
所以迫不及待地跑來玩～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好壯觀喔～！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望可以快點看到<delay20 />
很多蟲蟲在這裡開心生活的樣子～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" /><colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />開幕了～！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />空間又大，<delay8 />展覽室又多，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太驚人了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是這麼寬敞的地方，<delay20 />
就算把島上的蟲蟲都聚集在這裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們也能過得很舒適吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>